- Soft Contrast: #BFDBF7 (Columbia blue) and #E1E5F2 (Lavender) serve well as backgrounds or secondary UI elements, providing a calm, readable contrast.
- Financial Strength & Balance: #2E5339 (Cal Poly green) can reinforce growth, money, and resilience‚Äîperfect for charts, CTAs, or accent details.
